Вакансія від 17 березня 2020
Customer support representative (night shift)
12 000 – 15 000 грн
A1 Logistics Dnipro
Транспорт, логістика;
10–50 співробітників
Дніпро
Повна зайнятість, неповна зайнятість, готові взяти студента.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Опис вакансії
AS WE EXPAND WE ALSO LOOK FOR TALENTED CUSTOMER SUPPORT MANAGER WHO CAN WORK WITH CLIENTS DURING NIGHT SHIFT.WE ARE: AMERICAN LOGISTICS COMPANY: A1 Logistics TruckingSince 2006 we are developing the best shipping agency for the USA market, we have main office in Jacksonville, FL We are working for the U.S. market and we are looking for talented individuals with upper-intermediate and fluent English, who would work as shipping agents for our Dnipro or Zaporizhzhia (Ukraine) based branches.REQUIREMENTS: Advanced level of English with good communication skills, ability to learn quickly and work as a part of a team. If you speak Spanish and English it can help you to increase your salary.Scope of activities: — Calling prospective customers with a given pitch.• Arranging the transportation process• Guide the customer during the process of arranging the transportation• Conducting the process of transportation until the delivery.• Provide the best customer service over the phone, emails, text messages.• Manage all orders in our CRM system.• You going to be working with requests that are coming from the customers, so searching for new clients will not be within the scope of your activities.WHAT DO WE OFFER:Working schedule is 5 days a week Monday-Friday, from 10 PM — 5 AM.With a 35 min break for lunch.Especially when company covers half of the membership for the gym and of the payment for Spanish/English courses.Company pays for taxi that will bring you home after work as well company covers the fuel cost if you drive your own car.Company provides paid training program. During this program you will become experienced shipping agent and gain knowledge that is required to operate on American market.Office is located in the center of the city.Coffee, tea, snacks and fruits are always available in the officePaid vacation, legal employment.We consider only those candidates that send their CV in English to [відгукнутися]Feel free to get in contact with Yuliya
